  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in training matters that do not need access to HRMS e.g. register staff for external training courses; prepare documents to issue purchase orders for training courses, liaise with external training providers; staff nominations for trainings</li><li>Card access management</li><li>Updating of ITD and mobile claims for staff</li><li>Liaise with vendors on office equipment e.g. beverage machine, topping up of ingredient</li></ul><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong><br />Mondays to Thursdays: 8.30am to 6.00pm<br />Fridays: 8.30am to 5.30pm<br /><br /><strong>Salary: </strong>$15/hour<br /><strong>Contract Period: </strong>3 months to 1 year<br /><br />EA License No: 96C4864<br />Reg. No.: R24121728 EUNICE WOO JING QI</p>",
